value.string: Copied ETA Output Sheet Template to Output Folder
Copied Work Order from Template to Output
Copying BOMS Sheet to ETA Report Book

Set Arg  = WScript.Arguments
vExcel1 = Arg(0)
Dim xlapp ' as excel object 
Dim WSx, WSy ' as excel worksheet 
Dim x, y ' as workbook 
Set xlapp = CreateObject("Excel.Application")
Set x = xlapp.Workbooks.Open(vExcel1)
Set y = xlapp.Workbooks.Open("C:\Users\tgssupport\Documents\ETA_Reporting\Output\ETA Output Sheet template.xlsx") 
Set WSx = x.Worksheets("BOMS") 
Set WSy = y.Worksheets("Manufactured_Purchased Report")
WSx.Copy WSy ' copy worksheet to other workbook
Set WSx = nothing 
Set WSy = nothing 
y.Save 
y.close 
x.Save
x.Close
